Wordpress Connect is a WordPress plugin that integratesÂ Facebook Social Platform tools with WordPress. It provides tools to add the Facebook Like Button and Facebook Comments automatically to every post and page. Now your blog readers with a Facebook account can post comments, create discussions and like your posts.

The plugin also provides WordPress <a href="http://wp-connect.tomasvorobjov.com/docs/#widgets" rel="section" target="_blank">widgets</a> for the following Facebook Social Plugins:
<ul>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/activity/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Activity Feed</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/comments/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Comments</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/facepile/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Facepile</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/like-box/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Like Box</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/like/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Like Button</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/live-stream/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Live Stream</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/login/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Login Button</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/recommendations/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Recommendations</a></li>
	<li><a href="http://developers.facebook.com/docs/reference/plugins/send/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Send Button</a></li>
</ul>
These widgets can be placed into any available widgets area just as easy as any other WordPress Widget, i.e. through the widgets page (under Appearance on your Dashboard). 

For more information about how to use WordPress Connect, see the <a href="http://wp-connect.tomasvorobjov.com/docs">Documentation</a> pages.

Since version 2.0, WordPress Connect provides a simple yet powerful <a href="http://wp-connect.tomasvorobjov.com/api">API</a> for WordPress plugins and themes developers to integrate WordPress Connect with their plugins and themes.

